		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I had just clipped the /ce pin on the original mask rom, I wasn't aware you'd need a pull up resistor on an unattached pin.
<br />
<br />regardless, the case was glued shut early this week, so I'm not getting inside it again without damaging it further than I did opening it in the first place.
<br />
<br />Those famicom carts are hard to open without damaging.

		

